[Header] (fixed size, e.g. 32 bytes)
  - Magic bytes: "FRAC"
  - checksum
  - Version: u8
  - Body offset: u32
  - Footnotes offset: u32 # make sure this is stored in a way that works on all CPU archs
  - Reserved: [u8; 20]

[Body Section]
  - Raw or structured binary (e.g. paragraphs, spans)

[Footnotes Section]
  - footnote index table (with byte position refrences, a map basically)
  - List of footnotes with IDs and metadata